   "body" : "- make `v2transport` argument in `addconnection` RPC mandatory. https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/24748#discussion_r1470738750\r\n\t- previously it was an optional arg with default `false` value.\r\n\t- only place this RPC is used is in the [functional tests](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/11b436a66af3ceaebb0f907878715f331516a0bc/test/functional/test_framework/test_node.py#L742) where we always pass the appropriate `v2transport` option to the RPC anyways.\r\n- rename `v2_handshake()` to `_on_data_v2_handshake()` https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/24748#discussion_r1466958424\r\n- more compact return statement in `wait_for_reconnect()` https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/24748#discussion_r1466979708\r\n- assertion to check that empty version packets are received from `TestNode`.",
